=== Highlighting Nyarna
--- input
\declare:
  hl = \highlighter(nyarna):
  :text:|\t|
    \t
  :comment:|\c|
    <comment \c>
  :escape:|\e|
    <escape \e>
  :keyword:|\k|
    <keyword \k>
  :symref:|\s|
    <symref \s>
  :special:|\s|
    <special \s>
  :tag:|\t|
    <tag \t>
  \end(highlighter)
\end(declare)

\hl:<off>
  # comment
  Some text

  \declare:
    foo = \func:
      a: \Text
    :body:
      \a more \a
    \end(func)
  \end(declare)

  \block:<off>
    \no # nothing
  \end(block)
\end(hl)
--- output
<comment # comment>
Some text

<keyword \declare><special :>
  <symref foo> <special => <keyword \func><special :>
    <symref a><special :> <symref \Text>
  <special :><symref body><special :>
    <symref \a> more <symref \a>
  <keyword \end><special (><tag func><special )>
<keyword \end><special (><tag declare><special )>

<keyword \block><special :><special <><tag off><special >>
  \no #nothing
<keyword \end><special (><tag block><special )>